name: ProposalRocket
tag_list: sales, proposal, proposals, presentations, sales-proposal, proposalrocket, analytics
overview:
ProposalRocket is an online tool that allows users to create, manage and analyze sales proposals, access them remotely, and share templates with co-workers.

ProposalRocket is the best way to shorten the sales cycle. It integrates authoring, asset management, delivery and analytics tools in a single hosted environment that allows you to quickly create great looking proposals, store, tag and search your assets, collaborate with your colleagues, securely share your proposals in person or remotely and measure the results of your sales team.
